Module WitchHunt
Package fr.sos.witchhunt.model

Interface Visitor

All Known Implementing Classes:
ScoreCounter, ScoreCounter.ScoreBoard
public interface Visitor

Generic interface implemented by entities that visit visitables entities.

Implemented in particular by the game's ScoreCounter, which updates its score table by visiting players each time their score changes.

Defining a specific method for each class implementing Visitable is recommended if all Visitors can be lead to visiting them. Otherwise, create a new interface.
